title: 30 g Superglue Instant, Super Glue All Purpose, Strong Glue with Anticlog Cap, for Plastic, Glass, Ceramic, Metal, Wood, DIY, Precise Repair, Clear
features: Super Strong Glue: Our superglue have been tested to be super strong for all bonding processes that require a fast, strong bond, and their performance and ease of use make them ideal

All Purpose Glue: Bondtech super glue is suitable for bonding metal, ceramics, plastics, wood, glass, handicrafts, leather, rubber, etc., with a wide range of material compatibility, it is a good partner for every home, workshop, construction site and handicrafts, no need to worry about breakage

Precision Repair: Super glue all purpose comes with three droppers with tiny nozzles for faster and easier precision application in small, hard-to-reach areas. (Tip: After using the droppers, it is recommended to slightly vibrate the bottle vertically to avoid clogging of the droppers with residual strong glue; in addition, the tips of the droppers can be cut as needed)

Anti-clogging Design: The special cap design prevents the glue spout from sticking, prevents drying out, and is reusable. Superglue general strong can be used until the last drop and will not solidify
Heat Resistant & Waterproof: With a temperature resistance range of -40°C to +100°C, this all purpose glue is waterproof, dishwasher safe, fast drying, UV resistant and shock resistant when cured

Easy to Use: Keep the repair surface clean and dry before use. After applying the superglue for plastic, press and hold both repair surfaces for 45 seconds for initial curing. Wait 24 hours for optimum bonding
